  "prompt": "How can we find people on WhatsApp without their phone number?",
  "response": "Finding people on WhatsApp without their phone number can be a bit tricky since WhatsApp primarily relies on phone numbers for user identification. However, there are a few indirect methods you can try:\n\n### 1. **Using WhatsApp Business Directory**\n   - If the person you're looking for has a WhatsApp Business account, they might be listed in the WhatsApp Business directory. You can search for their business name or category within the app.\n\n### 2. **QR Code**\n   - If you have physical access to the person or their device, you can scan their WhatsApp QR code to add them as a contact. Here\u2019s how:\n     1. Open WhatsApp on your phone.\n     2. Go to **Settings** > **QR code** (or **Scan QR code**).\n     3. Scan the QR code from the other person\u2019s WhatsApp (they can find it in **Settings** > **QR code**).\n     4. This will add them to your contacts.\n\n### 3. **Group Chats**\n   - If you and the person are in the same WhatsApp group, you can find them in the group participants list and message them directly, even if they\u2019re not in your contacts.\n\n### 4. **Shared Links**\n   - The person might have shared a WhatsApp link (e.g., `https://wa.me/[phone number]`) on social media, a website, or elsewhere. Clicking on such a link can open a chat with them directly.\n\n### 5. **Mutual Contacts**\n   - If you have mutual friends or contacts, you can ask them to share the person's WhatsApp number with you.\n\n### 6. **Social Media or Websites**\n   - Some people share their WhatsApp contact information on social media profiles, websites, or forums. Look for such information if available.\n\n### 7. **Third-Party Apps**\n   - Be cautious with third-party apps or services claiming to help you find someone on WhatsApp without their number. Many of these are unreliable or pose privacy risks.\n\n### 8. **Username Search (Future Feature)**\n   - WhatsApp has been testing a username feature that will allow users to find others without sharing their phone numbers. If this feature becomes available, it might be the easiest way to find someone without their phone number.\n\n### Important Notes:\n- Always respect privacy and avoid misusing these methods.\n- Ensure you have the person\u2019s consent before adding or messaging them.\n\nIf none of these methods work, the only reliable way to connect with someone on WhatsApp is by obtaining their phone number.",
